{"tid":1393622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比卡超話要參考新疆模式","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:30:42.000Z","uid":239496,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"816e11f318de768fd2f7df03b386c73249305b6b","tid":1393622,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"比卡超又跳出黎，驚死俾蘆葦搶左c位，唔記得你先係送中主角，最大反派。<br />\n<br />\n保安局本身處理嘅事務，要成立一個「局」都浪費資源啦。仲要養一班睇住錦衣衛嘅太監。幾時光復保安局？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">東廠閹人</span>遠比光頭錦衣衛可怕，因為「中央」集權。皇帝隻狗都分級數，呢隻就係遺臭萬年級。<br />\n<br />\n比卡超意思係香港勇武派=新疆東突厥班友（塔利班嘅盟友，簡單啲講當我地係恐怖份子，所以反送中一開始黑警都係當一場<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰爭</span></span>黎打，而唔係示威遊行。"},{"pid":"321b29793513f8d05966860c58d045823d87d06d","tid":1393622,"uid":239496,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"補返篇報導<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Nb6Puw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Nb6Puw.png&h=19fcab21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CQuj9ux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCQuj9ux.png&h=9e121d0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66028118d863d05f7a72db4b53a1da3d58a4fcb9","tid":1393622,"uid":239496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"所以點解佢哋會買水炮車，就係為左有一日，有藉口用。<br />\n<br />\n而水炮車點解係實彈以外嘅最高武力？係因為水炮車=坦克車，但畫面好睇一百倍。亦都係偽戰爭級數最有利武器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CAXqkCP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCAXqkCP.png&h=eb05b480&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oR6Pv9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oR6Pv9.png&h=fba80239&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5eabbf9bac300a4fde9d59c0ec4b39ca0355a301","tid":1393622,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"仆街黃國健唔快d入去教育營住返一年半載？"},{"pid":"ab909bd51b7ed85607